\caption[Gene counts per MEI-type and non-human primate (NHP)]{\textbf{Gene counts per MEI-type and non-human primate (NHP)\\} Presented here are the number of genes analyzed between humans and the respective non-human primate. RheMac3: Rhesus Macaque; PonAbe2: Orangutan; GorGor3: Gorilla; PanTro4: Chimpanzee. Expression data: The genes with orthologs between humans and the non-human primate for which there was valid expression data. Filtered MEI: Genes containing mobile element insertions in humans but not the respecitive NHP, after filtering based on pylogenetic order.}
\label{table:mei}
